{"tid":2153390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［變相連儂牆？］喺蘋果落分類廣告有冇得諗","createTime":"2020-08-12T13:19:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T03:43:56.000Z","uid":171094,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7ebac5acf3c33d50128c86c232c89d9883666a1b","tid":2153390,"uid":171094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T13:19:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GwrkPMb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGwrkPMb.jpg&h=09ce58fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日蘋果分類廣告有人出咗抱緊自由呢格細廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一格仔可以落幾十字<br />\n仲要一格其實都只係幾十到100蚊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前一日晏晝send俾蘋果下一日就出到街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想大小小買兩格都只係兩嚿水有找<br />\n啲人搵工搵樓搵服務嗰陣又可以睇到文宣<br />\n效果可能都唔錯<br />\n多啲人知呢樣嘢又可以令黃店多啲喺度落廣告<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n長遠有一個地方俾人搵黃店服務/工作<br />\n同時又可以幫到蘋果<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14e2a8b1780ef9cf63ec571ff6161c2f28b7d087","tid":2153390,"uid":171094,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T13:19:56.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed49fc548928fdd9ab5bce656505ebcb449eba43","tid":2153390,"uid":171094,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T13:21:48.000Z","msg":"25萬份蘋果已變condom<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2153111\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2153111</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你哋唔係3分鐘熱度吓嘛？<br />\n快啲買晒佢"},{"pid":"d324dacc6fc41b751df2012ec53ffcd75dcca552","tid":2153390,"uid":171094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T13:22:42.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"